code: @Override public void reduce(Iterable<T> values, Collector<T> out) throws Exception {     int emitCnt = 0.     for (T val : values) {         out.collect(val).         emitCnt++.         if (emitCnt == count) {             break.         }     } }
@Override public void combine(Iterable<T> values, Collector<T> out) throws Exception {     reduce(values, out). }
